 <metadata>
  <name>Clough, Behind Tescos Back Via Highfield / Rectory</name>
  <desc>Enter the Clough through the Flower Garden. Run through the Clough turning right up Buckley Lane on to Clifton Road. Opposite the end of Arthur St take a left through the ginnel on the left onto West Road and then left onto Pinfold Drive all the way around the back of Tesco. Left up to the motorway roundabout and onto the other side of BNR behind the shops towards Cross Avenue. First right down Highfield Rd. Left onto Fairfax, right onto Rectory Lane all the way back to St Mary's Park.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Dale Richards</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/108724580"/>
  </author>
  <copyright author="OpenStreetMap contributors">
   <year>2020</year>
   <license>https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright</license>
  </copyright>
  <link href="https://www.strava.com/routes/3468212505158514640"/>
 </metadata>
